name: Concrete Cube
description:
Same materials, same colors but a totally different organization other air, other smells, other customs. 19 years old with the same vision of the world, small wonders but always very similar. After 14 hours of flight and a connection for the first time totally isolated, not knowing how to communicate and move around, I was sheltered for the first time to observe without speaking, without understanding, without interacting, just existing and looking at the small details that were familiar to me.

In collaboration with github.com/LucasRelva
